OL,4,G1905FDanger Man
OL,5,     GA foreign senator is murdered in
OL,6,     Gthe presence of his blind
OL,7,     Grelative, Josetta. Rioting ensues
OL,8,     Gdue to a rumor that the American
OL,9,     Ggovernment was behind the
OL,10,     Gkilling, and secret agent John
OL,11,     GDrake is sent in.
OL,12,G1935FDanger Man
OL,13,     GJohn Drake visits the Arabian
OL,14,     Gcoast to investigate illegal
OL,15,     Gslave trading. Disguised as a
OL,16,     Gslave trader himself, his
OL,17,     Gquestions meet with strong
OL,18,     Gresistance from both locals and
OL,19,     Gan Englishman.
